        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n> \n> Yep, Vijay is correct here.\n> We`re assigining the schema file to the eventListener interface version in VES configuration.\n> The schema file associated with VES Event Listener 7.2 spec needs to have a unique name.\n\nIt will have a unique name.  The intent of this commit was to establish a point to track changes.\n\nIf I change things as I'm copying things over to a new file, then it becomes very difficult to track what actually changed.  I don't mind changing the name of the file, but I think it would be easier to review if we track the content updates separately.",
